<li id="cite_note-55"><b><a href="#cite_ref-55" title="">^</a></b> The Christian concepts of <a href="/wiki/Heaven" title="Heaven">Heaven</a> and <a href="/wiki/Hell" title="Hell">Hell</a> do not translate directly into Hinduism. Spiritual realms such as <a href="/wiki/Vaikunta" title="Vaikunta">Vaikunta</a> (the abode of Vishnu) or <i>loka</i> are the closest analogues to an eternal Kingdom of God.</li>
